> Using String


```catala-metadata
#[test]
declaration scope S:
  output foo content String
  output bar content String
  output foo_lt_bar content boolean
  output foo_gt_bar content boolean
  output answer content String
  output answer_eq content boolean
  output answer_order content boolean
```


```catala
scope S:
  definition foo equals String.foo
  definition bar equals String.bar
  definition foo_lt_bar equals String.foo < bar
  definition foo_gt_bar equals foo > String.bar
  definition answer equals String.of_int of 42
  definition answer_eq equals answer = String.fortytwo
  definition answer_order equals String.of_int of 19 < answer and answer < String.of_int of 72
```
